    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_llm-raw-the-eye-o.O-Player%27s%20Options%20-%20Halflings.pdf_11_4",
    "text": "allows a traveler to walk or ride in the rain or snow without getting soaked to the bone. Wearers of these cloaks benefit from condition similar to that provided by endure elements, though it only protects from cold brought on specifically due to exposure to rain and/or snow.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
