  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_llm-raw-the-eye-o.O-Player%27s%20Options%20-%20Halflings.pdf_11_10",
    "text": "flutes, each of varying lengths, connected with leather bands. There are four fingerholes on the longest pipe, three on the shortest and none on the middle pipe. A single mouthpiece connects to all three pipes.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.511437908496732,
